          ],
          "referred_to_in": [],
          "citation_pdf_url": "https://www.legis.iowa.gov/docs/ico/section/2026/232.7.pdf"
        },
        {
          "number": "232.7A",
          "heading": "Rules of juvenile procedure",
          "body_text": "Proceedings under this chapter are subject to rules prescribed by the supreme court under section 602.4201.\n\n83 Acts, ch 186, §10058, 10201; §232.7A\nRules adopted by the supreme court are published in the compilation “Iowa Court Rules”",
