        {
          "number": "232.159",
          "heading": "Financial responsibility",
          "body_text": "Financial responsibility for any child placed pursuant to the provisions of the interstate compact on the placement of children under section 232.158 shall be determined in accordance with the provisions of article V of that interstate compact in the first instance. However, in the event of partial or complete default of performance thereunder, the provisions of chapters 252 and 252A, fixing responsibility for the support of children also may be invoked.\n\n85 Acts, ch 173, §30\nCS85, §232.159\neferred to in §232.166, 232.167",
          "body_chars": 527,
          "history_brackets": [
