        {
          "number": "257.23",
          "heading": "Form and time of return",
          "body_text": "The instructional support income surtax shall be made a part of the Iowa individual income tax return subject to the conditions and restrictions set forth in section 422.21.\n89 Acts, ch 135, §23",
