        {
          "number": "455B.192",
          "heading": "Local government — penalties",
          "body_text": "Notwithstanding sections 331.302, 331.307, 364.3, and 364.22, a city or county may assess a civil penalty for a violation of this subchapter III which is equal to the amount the department has assessed for a violation under this subchapter III.\n93 Acts, ch 137, §8;",
