        {
          "number": "709.18",
          "heading": "Sexual abuse of a corpse",
          "body_text": "1.  A person commits sexual abuse of a human corpse if the person knowingly and intentionally engages in a sex act, as defined in section 702.17, with a human corpse.\n  2.  A person who violates this section commits a class “D” felony.\n96 Acts, ch 1006, §1; ; eferred to in §692A.102",
          "body_chars": 283,
